results.name: Number of ways of writing n as a sum of 3 nonnegative cubes (counted naively).
link: Charles R Greathouse IV, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
program: (PARI) first(n)=my(s=vector(n+1)); for(k=0,sqrtnint(n,3), s[k^3+1]=1); Vec(Ser(s,,n+1)^3) \\ _Charles R Greathouse IV_, Sep 16 2016
